Big Brother Naija, BBNaija 2019 reality star, Ike Onyema has revealed why his relationship with Mercy Eke crashed. Recall that Ike and Mercy, BBNaija 2019 winner started romantic relationship on the reality show. The relationship became stronger up until sometime in later part of 2020. There were rumors that the lovebirds broke up after the couple engaged in an argument. However, Ike, finally confirming their break up, took to Twitter revealing why the relationship did not last. He wrote: “I am single because I showed more love in 2020 than I ever got back and I’m alright with that.”